title: "Teen Witches & Dog Psychics" (w/ Gabe Liedman)
itunes:title: "Teen Witches & Dog Psychics" (w/ Gabe Liedman)
description:
This week, Matt and Bowen are joined by truly wonderful beacon of joy Gabe Liedman, whose standup who had an IMPACT on the girls at a formative moment in their lives. They discuss writing for TV, the upcoming Q-Force (The pitch? "Netflix presents an animated Gay James Bond"! You already love!), The Craft, Scream, Fairuza Balk as a 90's icon, and ask the Star or Actress? question of Queen Neve Campbell. They also get into how Drew Barrymore is a one of a kind movie star, and are regaled with the tale of Gabe's experience with a dog psychic. Hear us out!!! Also: I Don't Think So Honeys that will shake you. Check out Gabe's podcast "I'm Afraid That..." on Lil Everywhere! Gabe Liedman is ALL OF US RIGHT NOW! SEND.
